2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on wireless networks and interference, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The concept of clustering in networks is discussed in the paper, which is a topic of interest in social and information networks. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper deals with interference among multiple agents (base stations), which falls under the scope of multiagent systems. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper uses mathematical models to analyze interference correlation, which involves the use of data structures and algorithms.
